    {
      "instruction": "<p>Peel and finely slice your <strong>brown onion[s]</strong></p><p>Heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) with a drizzle of <strong>vegetable oil</strong> and a small knob of <strong>butter</strong> over a medium heat</p><p>Once hot, add the <strong>sliced onion</strong> with a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and 1 tsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[1 1/2 tsp] </span><span class=\"text-danger\">[2 tsp]</span> <strong>sugar</strong></p><p>Cook for 8-10 min or until the onion has softened and caramelised – this is your <strong>caramelised onion</strong></p>",
      "order": 2,
      "media": {
