    {
      "instruction": "<p>Slice your <strong>brioche bun[s]</strong> in half</p><p>Remove the tray[s] with the fries from the oven and add the<strong> brioche halves </strong>(cut side up!) on top of the fries</p><p>Return the tray[s] to the oven for 4-5 min or until warmed through</p>",
