    {
      "instruction": "<p>To build the burger, top the <strong>warmed brioche base </strong>with your <strong>tomato ketchup</strong>, a <strong>outer lettuce leaf</strong>, 2 <strong>smashed patties</strong>, a dollop of <strong>cheese</strong> <strong>sauce</strong>, the <strong>caramelised</strong> <strong>onion</strong> and the <strong>warmed</strong> <strong>brioche</strong> <strong>lid</strong> – this is your <strong>smashed patty burger</strong></p><p>Serve the <strong>lettuce wedges </strong>and <strong>fries</strong> to the side, drizzle over the <strong>remaining cheese sauce </strong>and top with your <strong>crispy onions</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
